# Restic / B2 based backup
## Setup
- Copy the content into the target folder, i.e. ~/.backup
- Fill the details of the configuration files, assumption is you are running a backup into the EU instance of B2 and one on the US West one.
- Adjust the full-backup script for your specific use case
- Adjust the schedule.txt file with your preferred schedule
- Load the configuration with 
```
crontab schedule.txt
```

